Hello (Visitor)->(bold), welcome to SomMark!
SomMark is a clean, human-readable markup language designed for documentation.

To install the CLI:
@_code_@: sh
npm install -g sommark
smark --version
@_end_@

Next, create your first file:
@_code_@: sh
echo "[Doc]
Hello SomMark!
[end]" > example.smark
@_end_@

Now transpile it:
@_code_@: sh
smark --html ./example.smark -o output.html ./generate
@_end_@
`[Hello Adam]`
More info at (SomMark Docs)->(link:https://sommark.dev/docs).
